-- Hitachi, Johnson Controls tie up in batteries: report
-- 
-- Sun Oct 17, 2010 7:10pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/10/17/us-hitachi-johnson-idUSTRE69G1UA20101017

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Japan's Hitachi Ltd ( 6501.T ) will partner with U.S.-based Johnson Controls Inc ( JCI.N ) in lithium-ion and other advanced battery technologies, the Nikkei business daily reported on Monday. 

 (Reporting by Nobuhiro Kubo; Editing by  Edwina Gibbs )